caption: LOVE THIER FOOD! SO FRESH!
been going here for years. good Mexican food with a new modern design at the restaurant

I have ordered like 3-4 times already from this place and to be honest the food has not let me down everything is so delicious. I had tacos, nachos, picaditas, tortas, sopes, quesadilla and they have been sooo good. The only thing that’s a  little annoying is that every time I call to ordered and I give them my address the lady tells me they don’t deliver where i live, but am like I have ordered from here a couple of times. However they always end up delivering to me which is nice other people would of just hanged up so I appreciate that at least they do come here. Also the first time I ever order they send me a choco flan and the rice pudding cup both were soo yummy especially the flan. This time I just got the chocoflan, but it’s okay. I highly do recommend this place. The sopes, picaditas and quesadilla the tortilla is handmade which is wayyy better then the other ones a little bit more pricey, but worth it. Orchata and jamaica are good too give it a try.😋
